The paper proposes a novel approach for training autoencoders using adversarial training criterion. This is a common topic in the machine learning community, and the paper specifically focuses on image data. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper emphasizes the importance of capturing rich semantic representation of data, which suggests relevance to sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
